00:45:17,679 --> 00:45:18,679
Your father said

845
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:19,599
he doesn't want Dabao

846
00:45:19,599 --> 00:45:20,639
to stay in the mansion, either.

847
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:22,119
He said since your bother is gone,

848
00:45:22,880 --> 00:45:24,400
no need to make the living ones suffer.

849
00:45:26,159 --> 00:45:26,679
Stop.

850
00:45:27,519 --> 00:45:28,559
You really need a good beat!

851
00:45:30,159 --> 00:45:31,880
But he's my second brother after all.

852
00:45:46,920 --> 00:45:47,719
Where's Ruoruo?

853
00:45:49,039 --> 00:45:49,920
Where is she?

854
00:45:50,320 --> 00:45:51,360
She's probably idling around.

855
00:45:51,559 --> 00:45:52,000
Let her be.

856
00:45:52,880 --> 00:45:53,440
Have some fruit.

857
00:46:20,440 --> 00:46:20,920
Your Highness.

858
00:46:21,440 --> 00:46:23,320
The three-day punishment is over.

859
00:46:27,400 --> 00:46:28,639
Read these days' information

860
00:46:28,880 --> 00:46:29,719
to me.

861
00:46:30,079 --> 00:46:30,480
Yes.

862
00:46:35,440 --> 00:46:36,159
Recently,

863
00:46:36,360 --> 00:46:37,679
there have been hot debates
in the imperial court.

864
00:46:37,679 --> 00:46:39,480
We've achieved a complete victory
in the war against Beiqi.

865
00:46:42,480 --> 00:46:43,559
Now, many officials
from different ministries

866
00:46:43,599 --> 00:46:45,039
want to submit a joint memorial

867
00:46:45,480 --> 00:46:46,719
to advocate capturing Beiqi at one blow.

868
00:46:48,199 --> 00:46:49,960
The Second Prince is
contacting the Ministry of War.

869
00:46:53,239 --> 00:46:55,000
Fan Xian and Princess Wan'er

870
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:55,679
left the capital city.

871
00:46:58,360 --> 00:46:59,039
Where did they go?

872
00:46:59,559 --> 00:47:00,679
They left for an outing

873
00:47:01,119 --> 00:47:01,760
from the South Gate.

874
00:47:03,840 --> 00:47:04,519
The South Gate?

875
00:47:07,800 --> 00:47:09,079
Yesterday, the Empress Dowager...

876
00:47:11,480 --> 00:47:12,760
The Prime Minister visited

877
00:47:12,760 --> 00:47:13,519
Princess Wan'er last night.

878
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:15,679
How do we get the information?

879
00:47:16,400 --> 00:47:17,880
A little eunuch
from Imperial Clothes Division

880
00:47:18,239 --> 00:47:20,039
and a guard from the imperial residence

881
00:47:20,199 --> 00:47:20,920
are cousins.

882
00:47:21,480 --> 00:47:23,159
Last night, when visiting his cousin,

883
00:47:23,519 --> 00:47:24,719
the eunuch saw the Prime Minister

884
00:47:24,800 --> 00:47:26,159
entering the residence
in casual clothes.

885
00:47:26,800 --> 00:47:28,079
He reported the information
when he came back.

886
00:47:29,119 --> 00:47:30,639
So Lin Ruofu secretly visited

887
00:47:30,639 --> 00:47:31,519
Lin Wan'er late at night

888
00:47:31,519 --> 00:47:33,599
without telling anyone.

889
00:47:34,039 --> 00:47:35,599
Don't you find it weird?

890
00:47:37,880 --> 00:47:38,760
What's wrong?

891
00:47:41,760 --> 00:47:43,679
Will Lin Wan'er

892
00:47:43,840 --> 00:47:44,880
tell Fan Xian about it?

893
00:47:46,360 --> 00:47:48,760
Now the Prime Minister
roots for Fan Xian.

894
00:47:49,199 --> 00:47:50,519
Why should she hide it from him?

895
00:47:52,079 --> 00:47:52,800
Get the carriage ready!

896
00:47:53,920 --> 00:47:56,199
Your Highness, where are we going?

897
00:47:58,039 --> 00:47:58,880
Let's go for an outing.

898
00:48:03,800 --> 00:48:04,440
I've got it.

899
00:48:05,760 --> 00:48:06,239
Let me see!

900
00:48:06,639 --> 00:48:07,280
It's so heavy.

901
00:48:07,679 --> 00:48:08,280
Let me help you.

902
00:48:12,519 --> 00:48:13,719
What have you got?

903
00:48:22,559 --> 00:48:23,920
Don't tell anyone

904
00:48:23,920 --> 00:48:25,119
about my visit,

905
00:48:27,039 --> 00:48:28,079
especially Fan Xian.

906
00:48:30,119 --> 00:48:31,119
When you go outing tomorrow,

907
00:48:31,599 --> 00:48:32,760
do one thing for me.

908
00:48:34,800 --> 00:48:36,119
When you're out,

909
00:48:36,119 --> 00:48:38,320
find an excuse to go deep into the woods

910
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:40,760
with Fan Xian only.

911
00:48:42,079 --> 00:48:42,960
Remember that

912
00:48:43,639 --> 00:48:46,760
no matter what happens...

913
00:48:53,440 --> 00:48:54,639
What's wrong? Are you OK?

914
00:48:56,000 --> 00:48:57,559
I'm fine.

915
00:48:58,719 --> 00:48:59,559
How do you feel recently?

916
00:48:59,920 --> 00:49:00,639
Do you feel anything wrong?

917
00:49:02,239 --> 00:49:02,920
No.

918
00:49:04,159 --> 00:49:04,960
Nothing wrong.

919
00:49:16,719 --> 00:49:17,320
Got it!

920
00:49:18,119 --> 00:49:18,920
Put it down! Put it down! Put it down!

921
00:49:31,719 --> 00:49:32,440
The Assistant Minister
of the Ministry of Rites

922
00:49:32,440 --> 00:49:34,159
has come to offer
his condolences in person.

923
00:49:34,800 --> 00:49:35,719
Won't you see him?

924
00:49:36,599 --> 00:49:38,639
If I meet him, we will talk politely.

925
00:49:39,679 --> 00:49:41,599
He will say restrain your grief,
and I will say thank you.

926
00:49:43,199 --> 00:49:44,639
It's so boring.

927
00:49:45,719 --> 00:49:47,039
But you should be

928
00:49:47,360 --> 00:49:48,599
at the mourning hall.

929
00:49:50,199 --> 00:49:50,960
Will my son come back to life

930
00:49:52,519 --> 00:49:53,800
if I'm there?

931
00:50:00,199 --> 00:50:01,159
Have you sent out the men?

932
00:50:02,880 --> 00:50:05,280
They're all martial arts masters.
They're waiting outside the capital city.

933
00:50:06,320 --> 00:50:08,000
But Fan Xian and Wan'er

934
00:50:08,360 --> 00:50:09,320
have taken out many attendants.

935
00:50:10,199 --> 00:50:11,320
It won't be easy for them to attack.

936
00:50:12,760 --> 00:50:14,320
He will leave the crowd.

937
00:50:16,679 --> 00:50:17,840
What on earth are you going to do?

938
00:50:18,960 --> 00:50:20,800
By then, Fan Xian

939
00:50:21,239 --> 00:50:22,360
will be attacked.

940
00:50:23,159 --> 00:50:24,320
You should act as if you know nothing.

941
00:50:25,280 --> 00:50:26,639
Don't give yourself away.

942
00:50:27,159 --> 00:50:27,880
Don't you support Fan Xian

943
00:50:27,880 --> 00:50:28,920
all along?

944
00:50:29,119 --> 00:50:29,880
Haven't you entrusted Fan Xian

945
00:50:29,880 --> 00:50:30,800
with the future of

946
00:50:30,960 --> 00:50:31,920
the Lin family?

947
00:50:35,000 --> 00:50:38,480
I still don't know who killed Gong'er.

948
00:50:40,079 --> 00:50:41,320
I can trust the Lin family

949
00:50:41,320 --> 00:50:42,719
to an outsider.

950
00:50:43,400 --> 00:50:45,800
But I must

951
00:50:45,800 --> 00:50:47,360
remove all my doubts.

952
00:50:48,719 --> 00:50:50,800
Were you pretending to

953
00:50:52,000 --> 00:50:52,920
be supportive all these days?

954
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:53,920
Not really.

955
00:50:55,320 --> 00:50:58,400
If Fan Xian can pass this test,

956
00:50:59,320 --> 00:51:00,920
I really want to make him

957
00:51:01,800 --> 00:51:03,239
the backbone of the Lin family.

958
00:51:03,480 --> 00:51:04,840
The day the Second
Young Master was killed,

959
00:51:05,239 --> 00:51:07,280
Fan Xian really didn't
leave the capital city.

960
00:51:11,880 --> 00:51:13,440
I have a suspicion.

961
00:51:15,480 --> 00:51:17,239
What if there's
a hidden martial arts master

962
00:51:18,119 --> 00:51:19,480
by Fan Xian's side,

963
00:51:20,400 --> 00:51:21,320
a master who could

964
00:51:21,320 --> 00:51:23,519
match the Four Great Masters?

965
00:51:25,320 --> 00:51:26,519
Fan Xian was inside the capital city,

966
00:51:26,800 --> 00:51:29,000
but that martial arts master
killed Gong'er instead.

967
00:51:30,079 --> 00:51:31,159
According to Si Lili,

968
00:51:31,719 --> 00:51:33,159
she didn't tell Fan Xian

969
00:51:33,159 --> 00:51:33,960
the secret of the Second Young Master.

970
00:51:34,840 --> 00:51:36,960
Her words don't matter.

971
00:51:38,280 --> 00:51:39,440
As long as evidences show that

972
00:51:39,679 --> 00:51:40,840
there's a peerless martial arts master

973
00:51:40,840 --> 00:51:41,840
around Fan Xian,

974
00:51:42,159 --> 00:51:43,360
I can confirm that

975
00:51:43,800 --> 00:51:46,119
he's the one who killed Gong'er.

976
00:51:48,880 --> 00:51:50,320
This assassination

977
00:51:50,800 --> 00:51:52,679
is the final test.

978
00:51:54,039 --> 00:51:55,840
Dabao and Wan'er are also there.

979
00:51:56,159 --> 00:51:57,519
What if they get hurt...

980
00:51:59,320 --> 00:52:00,960
Because they are there,

981
00:52:01,119 --> 00:52:02,960
no one would believe that

982
00:52:03,599 --> 00:52:04,960
I'm the one who planned it.

983
00:52:08,639 --> 00:52:09,599
I hope there wouldn't be

984
00:52:09,599 --> 00:52:11,000
such a martial arts master.

985
00:52:20,239 --> 00:52:20,920
I've got it! I've got it!

986
00:52:22,000 --> 00:52:22,800
I told you.

987
00:52:22,880 --> 00:52:24,119
I don't lie.

988
00:52:24,360 --> 00:52:25,400
You got it, right?

989
00:52:30,159 --> 00:52:31,239
Now we've got two.

990
00:52:31,480 --> 00:52:32,480
It's your turn now.

991
00:52:34,599 --> 00:52:35,239
Watch me!

992
00:52:42,000 --> 00:52:42,480
What's up?

993
00:52:45,440 --> 00:52:46,320
I want to...

994
00:52:46,840 --> 00:52:47,480
You want what?

995
00:52:49,360 --> 00:52:50,960
I want to go somewhere quiet.

996
00:52:52,000 --> 00:52:52,679
Why?

997
00:52:54,039 --> 00:52:54,599
Wan'er.

998
00:52:57,000 --> 00:52:58,400
Here, it's for you!

999
00:53:00,079 --> 00:53:01,079
Where have you been?

1000
00:53:01,400 --> 00:53:02,760
The flower field over there.

1001
00:53:03,480 --> 00:53:04,800
Brother, stop sitting here as a fool.

1002
00:53:05,199 --> 00:53:06,360
Come with me to pick some flowers.

1003
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:07,760
You can make Wan'er a garland yourself.

1004
00:53:08,400 --> 00:53:08,840
OK.

1005
00:53:09,719 --> 00:53:10,840
Wan'er, wait for a moment.

1006
00:53:16,280 --> 00:53:18,159
Brother, I found the Taiping Residence.

1007
00:53:18,519 --> 00:53:20,039
Walk along the river to the east,
and you'll see it.

1008
00:53:20,440 --> 00:53:20,880
OK.

1009
00:53:22,039 --> 00:53:22,719
I'll go and see.

1010
00:53:22,719 --> 00:53:23,599
Stay here to cover me.

1011
00:53:24,199 --> 00:53:26,400
Brother, I'll go with you.

1012
00:53:35,760 --> 00:53:36,159
Hurry up!

1013
00:53:36,159 --> 00:53:36,960
Don't let them find out.

1014
00:54:01,039 --> 00:54:01,559
Listen!

1015
00:54:02,320 --> 00:54:03,760
When Fan Xian comes
into the woods alone,

1016
00:54:04,119 --> 00:54:04,880
we should spare no efforts
in striking him down.

1017
00:54:05,480 --> 00:54:05,880
Watch out!

1018
00:54:06,360 --> 00:54:07,480
Don't hurt our lady.

1019
00:54:07,599 --> 00:54:08,039
Do you understand?

1020
00:54:08,280 --> 00:54:08,679
Yes.

1021
00:54:12,679 --> 00:54:13,079
How's it going?

1022
00:54:13,440 --> 00:54:13,880
They are over there.

1023
00:54:14,000 --> 00:54:14,519
Have you seen Fan Xian?

1024
00:54:14,599 --> 00:54:16,039
I only saw our lady.
Fan Xian was not there.

1025
00:54:16,159 --> 00:54:16,519
What?

1026
00:54:17,719 --> 00:54:18,559
You didn't see Fan Xian.

1027
00:54:19,519 --> 00:54:19,840
Right.

1028
00:54:20,000 --> 00:54:21,559
I sneaked over

1029
00:54:21,840 --> 00:54:23,679
and saw our lady
and the First Young Master.

1030
00:54:24,039 --> 00:54:25,480
But Fan Xian was not there.

1031
00:54:27,360 --> 00:54:28,559
What's happening?

1032
00:54:30,960 --> 00:54:31,440
Don't be nervous.

1033
00:54:32,800 --> 00:54:34,400
We'll wait till he shows up.

1034
00:54:35,039 --> 00:54:35,440
Go and check again.

1035
00:54:36,079 --> 00:54:36,440
Yes.

1036
00:54:44,679 --> 00:54:45,480
It's right ahead.

1037
00:54:47,039 --> 00:54:48,079
My mom used to live

1038
00:54:48,079 --> 00:54:48,800
in the Taiping Residence.

1039
00:54:49,360 --> 00:54:50,039
I can't let others know

1040
00:54:50,039 --> 00:54:50,840
I've been here.

1041
00:54:51,159 --> 00:54:52,440
So I came up with the idea
of going for an outing.

1042
00:54:53,280 --> 00:54:53,800
I know.

1043
00:54:54,119 --> 00:54:55,239
Your secret is safe with me.

1044
00:54:55,599 --> 00:54:56,639
Uncle Wuzhu will be here in a moment.

1045
00:54:56,880 --> 00:54:57,599
You haven't met yet.

1046
00:54:58,199 --> 00:54:59,960
Is he easy to get along?

1047
00:55:00,119 --> 00:55:00,840
He seldom talks.

1048
00:55:02,039 --> 00:55:03,639
Are you here to mourn her?

1049
00:55:04,039 --> 00:55:05,079
No, we're here for a key.

1050
00:55:07,599 --> 00:55:08,360
A key?

1051
00:55:11,400 --> 00:55:12,159
It's right ahead.

1052
00:55:18,079 --> 00:55:19,480
Brother, here it is.

1053
00:55:21,000 --> 00:55:22,599
My mom used to live here.

1054
00:55:27,400 --> 00:55:28,559
There's no weed on the walls.

1055
00:55:29,119 --> 00:55:30,119
It is well cleaned.

1056
00:55:31,159 --> 00:55:33,239
Perhaps someone lives here.

1057
00:55:33,719 --> 00:55:34,199
No.

1058
00:55:35,199 --> 00:55:36,440
If someone lives here,

1059
00:55:36,519 --> 00:55:37,039
there should be smoke rising from

1060
00:55:37,039 --> 00:55:38,199
the chimney right now.

1061
00:55:39,360 --> 00:55:41,239
Maybe he eats early.

1062
00:55:46,519 --> 00:55:47,920
It's so quiet around.

1063
00:55:48,000 --> 00:55:49,199
Not even a chirp from birds.

1064
00:55:56,039 --> 00:55:57,519
Brother, look.

1065
00:55:57,719 --> 00:55:58,719
The flowers here are really beautiful.

1066
00:55:59,000 --> 00:56:00,599
Let's fetch some for my sister-in-law.

1067
00:56:02,360 --> 00:56:03,320
After all, we told her

1068
00:56:03,320 --> 00:56:04,360
we're here to pick flowers.

1069
00:56:04,840 --> 00:56:05,719
Let's hurry back.

1070
00:56:05,960 --> 00:56:06,760
Don't keep them waiting.

1071
00:56:07,000 --> 00:56:07,360
Here you are.

1072
00:56:36,440 --> 00:56:36,880
Come back!

1073
00:56:43,199 --> 00:56:44,519
Your Highness!

1074
00:56:45,280 --> 00:56:46,119
Cousin.

1075
00:56:46,800 --> 00:56:47,440
Where's Fan Xian?

1076
00:56:48,039 --> 00:56:49,039
He went to pick flowers.

1077
00:56:49,400 --> 00:56:50,119
Do you want to see him?

1078
00:56:50,840 --> 00:56:52,480
All rise. No need to make a fuss.

1079
00:56:56,320 --> 00:56:57,239
Let's go for a walk.

1080
00:57:02,760 --> 00:57:04,199
When Fan Xian gets back,
ask him to wait for me.

1081
00:57:05,079 --> 00:57:05,599
OK.

1082
00:57:17,719 --> 00:57:19,159
What time is it?

1083
00:57:24,280 --> 00:57:25,199
It's time.

1084
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:28,000
What if they fail?

1085
00:57:30,039 --> 00:57:31,000
They were kept

1086
00:57:31,000 --> 00:57:32,079
outside the capital city before.

1087
00:57:32,079 --> 00:57:33,000
Even if they fail,

1088
00:57:33,400 --> 00:57:34,519
they won't get us in trouble.

1089
00:57:35,000 --> 00:57:36,880
Moreover,

1090
00:57:37,599 --> 00:57:39,920
they've never seen Fan Xian before.

1091
00:57:40,719 --> 00:57:41,679
They won't give themselves away.

1092
00:57:46,400 --> 00:57:49,159
Master, you've helped me a lot.

1093
00:57:55,280 --> 00:57:56,440
What if there's no martial arts master

1094
00:57:56,559 --> 00:57:58,320
by Fan Xian's side?

1095
00:57:59,880 --> 00:58:01,480
Then I'm afraid

1096
00:58:03,000 --> 00:58:05,519
I will never know who killed Gong'er.

1097
00:58:08,760 --> 00:58:09,559
Boss!

1098
00:58:09,880 --> 00:58:10,519
What's up?

1099
00:58:11,039 --> 00:58:11,639
He left.

1100
00:58:11,679 --> 00:58:12,360
Who left?

1101
00:58:12,679 --> 00:58:14,719
Our lady and a young man

1102
00:58:15,360 --> 00:58:16,039
left alone.

1103
00:58:18,280 --> 00:58:18,679
Let's go!

1104
00:58:29,840 --> 00:58:32,079
Cousin, where are your guards?

1105
00:58:32,719 --> 00:58:33,760
My carriage is stopped far away.

1106
00:58:35,400 --> 00:58:36,719
You're too incautious.

1107
00:58:36,920 --> 00:58:38,599
We can't talk with them around.

1108
00:58:39,920 --> 00:58:42,079
Cousin, what do you want to talk about?

1109
00:58:47,239 --> 00:58:48,320
What on earth did your father

1110
00:58:49,000 --> 00:58:50,159
tell you last night?

1111
00:58:52,519 --> 00:58:53,280
Let me guess.

1112
00:58:55,079 --> 00:58:57,119
Your father is still suspicious of

1113
00:58:57,119 --> 00:58:58,599
Fan Xian.

1114
00:58:58,920 --> 00:58:59,559
Right?

1115
00:59:02,719 --> 00:59:03,719
It's an easy guess.

1116
00:59:04,599 --> 00:59:06,440
Your father acts cautiously
all his life,

1117
00:59:07,400 --> 00:59:08,880
but he trusts Fan Xian

1118
00:59:09,320 --> 00:59:10,159
too easily.

1119
00:59:11,719 --> 00:59:14,440
It must be hard for you.

1120
00:59:23,199 --> 00:59:25,400
Brother, I can't see the archer.

1121
00:59:25,760 --> 00:59:26,400
Stay where you are.

1122
00:59:26,719 --> 00:59:27,079
Brother!

1123
00:59:28,400 --> 00:59:29,920
